name: Baytech Webs
overview:
Baytech Web Design started as a web design firm in 2001. In 2008, Baytech Web Design became a full service web design, web applications and online marketing solutions firm that delivers measurable results to its many clients, spanning all manner of industries.

Baytech Web Design changed its name to Baytech Webs in early 2007. It expanded its professional staff of in-house designers and project managers to 50 programmers, developers, project managers, designers, copywriters and web online solution strategists. In addition, they also expanded their services to include more new strategies that contribute to the success and profitability of the companies they contract with.

Baytech Web Design has been ranked as Silicon Valleyâ€™s #1 Top Web Design Firm by the Silicon Valley Business Journal on June 20th 2008. Baytech Web Design earned Golden Horizon Interactive Award in December 2007 and December 2008 for being a premier Web Design firm.

From year 2006 to 2008, Baytech Webs has produced about 500 microsites, portals, ecommerce web site, and intranet sites. Baytech Webs expanded the services to web 2.0 portal application development and focus on growing its on-line marketing solutions. Baytech Webs received several awards recognizing their creative talent and exemplary work.
